      "content": "i dont even know why im bothering anymore. it's just the same thing every single time. i try to fix my life, i try to get a job, i try to be better, and then i just crash and everything falls apart again. it feels like i'm just stuck in this loop and it never ever changes. i am so tired of trying.",
