      "content": "Breaking a cycle that feels inescapable often requires a complete shift in perspective rather than just trying harder; sometimes the only way to stop the pain is to let go of the need for a solution and simply accept the moment as it is. You don't have to fix your life right now, or even decide what your future looks like, because forcing a path through the darkness only makes the darkness seem more solid. The most powerful thing you can do is to stop fighting the loop and instead find a way to let the loop end, even if that means letting go of everything you've ever known.",
